338
00:18:12,540 --> 00:18:14,259
I pulled a little trick.

339
00:18:14,260 --> 00:18:16,410
I shifted the blame elsewhere.

340
00:18:16,780 --> 00:18:19,770
I said he insisted on
taking the Linyi slave away.

341
00:18:20,100 --> 00:18:22,330
Now, all the heat is on him.

342
00:18:22,780 --> 00:18:24,250
Tough luck for the guy.

343
00:18:31,060 --> 00:18:32,250
My dear,

344
00:18:33,260 --> 00:18:34,530
one day,

345
00:18:36,340 --> 00:18:38,330
I'll pluck the moon down just for you.

346
00:18:38,980 --> 00:18:40,930
