355
00:19:01,180 --> 00:19:02,499
After the Qijing Pavilion fire,

356
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:04,610
He Youguang gained the most.

357
00:19:05,380 --> 00:19:06,810
Big profit breeds suspicion.

358
00:19:06,900 --> 00:19:07,739
If our guess is right,

359
00:19:07,740 --> 00:19:08,779
and He Youguang is behind

360
00:19:08,780 --> 00:19:11,090
Haihu's death,

361
00:19:11,140 --> 00:19:12,059
then Amita

362
00:19:12,060 --> 00:19:14,419
has spent years grateful to the man

363
00:19:14,420 --> 00:19:16,019
who killed her father.

364
00:19:16,020 --> 00:19:17,890
She will definitely turn on him.

365
00:19:17,940 --> 00:19:19,419
Then, we can win her over

366
00:19:19,420 --> 00:19:21,530
and get all the evidence on He Youguang.

367
00:19:22,420 --> 00:19:24,010
I can get close to her,

368
00:19:24,060 --> 00:19:25,930
but I need a reason.

369
00:19:26,170 --> 00:19:27,499
I told He Youguang

370
00:19:27,500 --> 00:19:28,699
I'm just wandering the world,

371
00:19:28,700 --> 00:19:30,530
not getting involved in his affairs.

372
00:19:31,460 --> 00:19:32,650
So,

373
00:19:33,140 --> 00:19:35,099
how do I get close
without raising suspicion?

374
00:19:35,100 --> 00:19:37,730
An unmarried man doesn't need a reason

375
