to approach an unmarried woman.

376
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:44,210
"When a gentleman sees
a lovely lady, he longs for her."

377
00:19:47,060 --> 00:19:48,570
Romance?

378
00:19:50,820 --> 00:19:52,770
It's just for show.

379
00:19:53,340 --> 00:19:54,899
At Chang'an banquets,

380
00:19:54,900 --> 00:19:55,419
