382
00:19:56,740 --> 00:19:59,050
This is your moment to shine.

383
00:19:59,220 --> 00:20:00,410
No.

384
00:20:01,140 --> 00:20:03,090
I'm just afraid Amita might

385
00:20:03,820 --> 00:20:05,410
fall too deep.

386
00:20:06,660 --> 00:20:08,090
Seriously, don't laugh.

387
00:20:09,180 --> 00:20:10,779
I don't mind being called

388
00:20:10,780 --> 00:20:12,050
a heartless scoundrel.

389
00:20:12,220 --> 00:20:13,979
But, it wouldn't be fair to her.

390
00:20:13,980 --> 00:20:15,739
Then, you are underestimating Amita.

391
00:20:15,740 --> 00:20:17,330
And you are underestimating me.

392
00:20:18,100 --> 00:20:19,290
Fine.

393
00:20:19,740 --> 00:20:21,139
I admit you're charming,

394
00:20:21,140 --> 00:20:23,539
smart, and quick to adapt.

395
00:20:23,540 --> 00:20:25,099
But Amita is sharp-minded

396
00:20:25,100 --> 00:20:27,139
and ruthless when she needs to be.

397
00:20:27,140 --> 00:20:29,490
She wouldn't easily
hand her heart to anyone.

398
00:20:29,900 --> 00:20:31,930
That's why you are
the right one for this.

