401
00:20:37,420 --> 00:20:37,979
Maybe...

402
00:20:37,980 --> 00:20:39,170
What?

403
00:20:39,780 --> 00:20:41,499
Why are you trying to avoid it?

404
00:20:41,500 --> 00:20:42,979
Don't tell me you've fallen

405
00:20:42,980 --> 00:20:44,939
for someone in Lingnan?
Is that it?

406
00:20:44,940 --> 00:20:46,250
I'll do it.

407
00:20:48,140 --> 00:20:50,699
He Youguang will be at the horse ranch
in the west of the city.

408
00:20:50,700 --> 00:20:52,019
I hear Amita will be there to help

409
00:20:52,020 --> 00:20:53,610
pick horses.

410
00:20:53,660 --> 00:20:55,139
It's the perfect chance

411
00:20:55,140 --> 00:20:56,410
to introduce yourself.

412
00:20:57,060 --> 00:20:58,619
Straw sandals!

413
00:20:58,620 --> 00:21:00,690
Straw sandals! Hemp sandals!

414
00:21:01,460 --> 00:21:03,810
Straw sandals! Hemp sandals!

415
00:21:04,860 --> 00:21:07,050
- Here for a pair of sandals?
- How much?

416
00:21:07,260 --> 00:21:08,019
One copper coin.

417
00:21:08,020 --> 00:21:08,979
One copper coin.

418
00:21:08,980 --> 00:21:09,459
Here, Gou.

419
00:21:09,460 --> 00:21:10,419
These sandals

420
00:21:10,420 --> 00:21:11,579
are comfy and durable.

421
00:21:11,580 --> 00:21:12,659
For me?

422
00:21:12,660 --> 00:21:13,850
Yes.

423
00:21:17,700 --> 00:21:18,739
See if they fit.

424
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:19,339
Perfect!

425
00:21:19,340 --> 00:21:20,570
Thank you, Qilang!

426
00:21:22,340 --> 00:21:23,099
One coin?

427
00:21:23,100 --> 00:21:24,179
One copper coin.

428
00:21:24,180 --> 00:21:25,379
How is business today?

429
00:21:25,380 --> 00:21:26,570
Not bad.

430
00:21:34,420 --> 00:21:35,379
What's this?

431
00:21:35,380 --> 00:21:36,499
Roasted bamboo rat.

432
00:21:36,500 --> 00:21:37,099
Bamboo rat?

433
00:21:37,100 --> 00:21:38,290
Bamboo rat.

434
00:21:40,740 --> 00:21:41,930
Enjoy your meal.

435
00:21:45,860 --> 00:21:47,490
These days, my mood

436
00:21:48,420 --> 00:21:50,290
is like the mountains in Lingnan.

437
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:51,890
It's all ups and downs.

438
00:21:52,900 --> 00:21:54,530
Not a moment of peace.

439
00:21:55,340 --> 00:21:57,170
When Ma Guiyun was burned alive,

440
00:21:57,420 --> 00:21:58,930
I cursed the heavens,

441
00:21:59,820 --> 00:22:01,930
blaming fate for
dragging me into this mess.

442
00:22:02,260 --> 00:22:03,450
But now I'm glad.

443
00:22:03,940 --> 00:22:04,579
I've been

444
00:22:04,580 --> 00:22:06,650
led step by step toward the truth.

445
00:22:06,820 --> 00:22:08,490
I have just one goal.

446
00:22:09,020 --> 00:22:10,210
To avenge my father.

447
00:22:10,380 --> 00:22:12,170
That grudge must be repaid.

448
00:22:12,460 --> 00:22:14,619
But, carrying that burden

449
00:22:14,620 --> 00:22:15,779
has stripped you

450
00:22:15,780 --> 00:22:17,490
of your carefree charm.

451
00:22:17,540 --> 00:22:18,850
And it breaks my heart.

452
00:22:25,140 --> 00:22:27,099
All the more reason

453
00:22:27,100 --> 00:22:28,779
I need to succeed in

454
00:22:28,780 --> 00:22:29,970
this fake romance.

455
00:22:31,860 --> 00:22:34,250
You'd hung around banquets in Chang'an,

456
00:22:34,540 --> 00:22:36,450
but you've never had real love.

457
00:22:37,140 --> 00:22:39,850
So, how would you know how to woo a woman?

458
00:22:42,020 --> 00:22:43,890
Your smile is awful, you know.

459
00:22:43,980 --> 00:22:45,690
I don't know how to charm women?

460
00:22:46,220 --> 00:22:48,339
Love is hard, but I'll survive.

461
00:22:48,340 --> 00:22:49,499
I just usually

462
00:22:49,500 --> 00:22:50,659
don't mess around.

463
00:22:50,660 --> 00:22:51,930
I don't flirt for fun.

464
00:22:52,220 --> 00:22:52,739
Laugh again,

465
00:22:52,740 --> 00:22:53,779
and I'll slap you silly.

466
00:22:53,780 --> 00:22:54,379
Yes.

467
00:22:54,380 --> 00:22:55,659
You are charming and suave,

468
00:22:55,660 --> 00:22:56,659
and every word is a gem.

469
00:22:56,660 --> 00:22:58,690
Every lady you meet just lights up.

470
00:22:59,340 --> 00:23:01,290
I'll go save the damsel next.

471
00:23:09,380 --> 00:23:10,379
She will be

472
00:23:10,380 --> 00:23:11,810
head over heels for me.

473
00:23:19,420 --> 00:23:21,410
I swear I'll give you a slap.

474
00:23:24,420 --> 00:23:26,010
Splendid!

475
00:23:28,140 --> 00:23:29,330
Trust me, Zhao.

476
00:23:29,380 --> 00:23:31,019
In all of Lingnan,

477
00:23:31,020 --> 00:23:32,890
Amita is the best rider.

478
00:23:32,900 --> 00:23:35,370
Best horse picker? Also Amita.

479
00:23:35,740 --> 00:23:36,499
Sometimes I wonder,

480
00:23:36,500 --> 00:23:38,699
what's Li Shande even doing?

481
00:23:38,700 --> 00:23:41,290
Where is he supposed to get his horses?

482
00:23:42,380 --> 00:23:44,530
I'm honestly stressed on his behalf.

483
00:23:45,700 --> 00:23:47,050
I've planned it out.

484
00:23:47,300 --> 00:23:48,139
When the time comes,

485
00:23:48,140 --> 00:23:49,850
I'll gift him a basket.

486
00:23:50,140 --> 00:23:52,499
I'll look him dead in the eye and say,

487
00:23:52,500 --> 00:23:53,659
"Mr. Li,

488
00:23:53,660 --> 00:23:55,579
why don't you just carry your litchis

489
00:23:55,580 --> 00:23:57,330
on your back to Chang'an?"

490
00:23:58,300 --> 00:23:59,570
He will die from exhaustion!

491
00:24:00,220 --> 00:24:01,659
No more horses for him,

492
00:24:01,660 --> 00:24:03,370
but mules!

493
00:24:05,980 --> 00:24:08,730
He really thinks we're all fools.

494
00:24:10,140 --> 00:24:11,850
Wisdom in foolishness, right?

495
00:24:12,740 --> 00:24:15,490
Big wisdom means intense ignorance.

496
00:24:15,980 --> 00:24:18,770
Real wisdom is real ignorance.

497
00:24:19,020 --> 00:24:22,010
The dumber you look,
the smarter you must be.

498
00:24:22,980 --> 00:24:25,050
I mean, take my brilliance.

499
00:24:25,780 --> 00:24:28,850
Who here is sharp enough to see it?

500
00:24:29,340 --> 00:24:32,970
No one gets it but me.

501
00:24:33,740 --> 00:24:35,210
It's all up in the brain.

502
00:24:42,620 --> 00:24:43,810
Good.

503
00:24:48,260 --> 00:24:49,059
Guiyun.

504
00:24:49,060 --> 00:24:50,330
Inspector He.

505
00:24:51,180 --> 00:24:52,970
- Chief Scribe Zhao.
- Guiyun.

506
00:24:53,220 --> 00:24:53,979
As we came down,

507
00:24:53,980 --> 00:24:55,779
I thought those two

508
00:24:55,780 --> 00:24:56,939
looked familiar.

509
00:24:56,940 --> 00:24:58,890
Didn't expect it to really be you.

510
00:24:59,260 --> 00:25:01,010
- What are the odds?
- Yeah.

511
00:25:01,140 --> 00:25:02,339
My goddaughter

512
00:25:02,340 --> 00:25:03,619
