513
00:25:03,620 --> 00:25:04,930
So we swing by here

514
00:25:05,020 --> 00:25:06,810
whenever to admire the performance.

515
00:25:08,220 --> 00:25:10,330
Guiyun, what brings you here?

516
00:25:10,380 --> 00:25:13,859
I'm looking to pick out a fast steed

517
00:25:13,860 --> 00:25:15,050
just for fun.

518
00:25:16,820 --> 00:25:17,299
That means

519
00:25:17,300 --> 00:25:19,730
Guiyun is a master rider, huh?

520
00:25:19,940 --> 00:25:21,259
