522
00:25:23,340 --> 00:25:25,939
And back in Chang'an,
I loved horseback riding.

523
00:25:25,940 --> 00:25:27,250
My nickname was

524
00:25:27,260 --> 00:25:28,530
"Sassy Rider."

525
00:25:29,020 --> 00:25:30,290
The steed and I are one.

526
00:25:30,340 --> 00:25:32,610
I rode six horses
straight into the ground.

527
00:25:33,380 --> 00:25:34,570
Six of them?

528
00:25:35,420 --> 00:25:36,610
Impressive.

529
00:25:36,740 --> 00:25:37,699
That means

530
00:25:37,700 --> 00:25:39,970
we're in for a real treat today.

531
00:25:40,060 --> 00:25:41,339
Why don't you do a few laps

532
00:25:41,340 --> 00:25:42,139
with Amita later?

533
00:25:42,140 --> 00:25:43,450
Have a little match.

534
00:25:43,540 --> 00:25:45,530
I have two wild horses here

535
00:25:45,580 --> 00:25:47,499
that just broke

536
00:25:47,500 --> 00:25:49,610
