537
00:25:49,660 --> 00:25:51,650
Help me break them in, will you?

538
00:25:51,660 --> 00:25:52,139
I...

539
00:25:52,140 --> 00:25:53,219
You got this.

540
00:25:53,220 --> 00:25:55,179
No, back then I was thinner.

541
00:25:55,180 --> 00:25:56,610
Now I'm...

542
00:25:57,700 --> 00:25:59,050
Plus, look at her!

543
00:25:59,260 --> 00:26:01,059
She rides like a warrior queen.

544
00:26:01,060 --> 00:26:02,770
She looks amazing on a horse.

545
00:26:02,780 --> 00:26:03,979
Me going up against her?

546
00:26:03,980 --> 00:26:05,819
That's not even a fair fight.

547
00:26:05,820 --> 00:26:07,010
Oh, it's fair.

548
00:26:07,380 --> 00:26:08,930
Amita!

549
00:26:09,700 --> 00:26:10,930
Come back here.

550
00:26:11,540 --> 00:26:12,730
Come back!

551
00:26:13,260 --> 00:26:15,290
Look at her skills!

552
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:17,970
Come on.

553
00:26:18,700 --> 00:26:22,050
In all of Lingnan, no one rides better.

554
00:26:22,460 --> 00:26:23,650
Don't you forget it.

555
00:26:23,860 --> 00:26:25,730
My goddaughter, Amita, is the best.

